olcano-sh/agentcube`\n**Go version:** 1.25.0\n\n---\n\n### 2. Top-Level Directory Structure (Workspace)\n\n```\nworkspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/\n├── .sdd_prompt.md           # SDD prompt template for generating delta-specs\n├── changes/                  # AR (Architecture Record) change directories\n│   ├── AR-001/              # CRD AgentRuntime type definition\n│   ├── AR-002/              # CRD CodeInterpreter type definition\n│   ├── AR-003/              # CRD shared types and constants\n│   ├── AR-004/              # WorkloadManager HTTP service framework\n│   └── AR-005/              # Sandbox creation handler\n├── client-go/                # Generated Kubernetes typed client, informers, listers\n├── delta-spec.md             # Root-level delta spec for AR-004\n├── design.md                 # AR-003 design document\n├── go.mod / go.sum           # Go module definition\n├── pkg/                      # Go packages\n│   ├── apis/runtime/v1alpha1/  # CRD type definitions\n│   └── workloadmanager/        # WorkloadManager HTTP service\n├── project.md                # OpenSpec project context\n├── test_spec.md              # TDD test case specification\n└── [feature dirs]/           # ci-cd/, cli-toolkit/, code-execution/, deployment/,\n                              # idle-cleanup/, integrations/, python-sdk/,\n                              # sandbox-orchestration/, session-routing/, session-store/, testing/\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. The `pkg/workloadmanager` Module\n\n#### 3.1 Current Files\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/response/response.go` | HTTP response helpers |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/response/response_test.go` | Response helper tests |\n\n**Note:** The `workloadmanager` module is only partially implemented. Per the AR-004 design document, the full planned structure is:\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n├── server.go                    # Server struct, NewServer(), Run(), Shutdown()\n├── config.go                    # Config struct, defaults, env var loading\n├── routes.go                    # SetupRoutes(engine *gin.Engine, deps *Dependencies)\n├── handler/\n│   ├── health.go                # GET /healthz, GET /readyz\n│   ├── agent_runtime.go         # AgentRuntime CRUD handlers\n│   └── code_interpreter.go      # CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers\n├── middleware/\n│   └── request_id.go            # X-Request-ID tracking middleware\n├── response/\n│   └── response.go              # JSON(), Error(), Created() helpers [EXISTS]\n├── server_test.go\n├── config_test.go\n├── routes_test.go\n├── handler/\n│   ├── health_test.go\n│   ├── agent_runtime_test.go\n│   └── code_interpreter_test.go\n└── response/\n    └── response_test.go         [EXISTS]\n```\n\n#### 3.2 Existing Types/Interfaces in `response/response.go`\n\n```go\ntype SuccessResponse struct {\n    Data    interface{} `json:\"data\"`\n    Message string      `json:\"message,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype ErrorResponse struct {\n    Error     string `json:\"error\"`\n    Code      int    `json:\"code\"`\n    RequestID string `json:\"request_id,omitempty\"`\n}\n\nfunc JSON(c *gin.Context, code int, data interface{})\nfunc Created(c *gin.Context, data interface{})\nfunc Error(c *gin.Context, httpCode int, code int, message string)\nfunc ErrorWithID(c *gin.Context, httpCode int, code int, message string, requestID string)\n```\n\n#### 3.3 Planned Types (from AR-004 design.md)\n\n```go\ntype Config struct {\n    Port         int\n    KubeConfig   string\n    Namespace    string\n    ResyncPeriod time.Duration\n    Debug        bool\n}\n\ntype Server struct {\n    config  *Config\n    engine  *gin.Engine\n    httpSrv *http.Server\n    deps    *Dependencies\n}\n\ntype Dependencies struct {\n    Clientset   clientset.Interface\n    Informer    informers.SharedInformerFactory\n    ARLister    runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n    CILister    runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. The `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` Module (CRD Types)\n\n#### 4.1 Files\n\n| File | Path |\n|------|------|\n| `agent_type.go` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go` |\n| `codeinterpreter_types.go` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` |\n| `shared_types.go` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` |\n| `constants.go` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants.go` |\n| `groupversion_info.go` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` |\n| `doc.go` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` |\n| `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` |\n\n#### 4.2 Key Types Defined\n\n**AgentRuntime CRD:**\n```go\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta\n    metav1.ObjectMeta\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort\n    Template           *SandboxTemplate   // embeds corev1.PodSpec\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration   // default: 15m\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration   // default: 8h\n}\n\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels, Annotations map[string]string\n    Spec        corev1.PodSpec\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeList struct { ... }\n```\n\n**CodeInterpreter CRD:**\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreter struct { ... }\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort\n    Template           *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate  // flat fields (not PodSpec)\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration\n    WarmPoolSize       *int32\n    AuthMode           AuthModeType\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels, Annotations  map[string]string\n    RuntimeClassName     *string\n    Image                string\n    ImagePullPolicy      corev1.PullPolicy\n    ImagePullSecrets     []corev1.LocalObjectReference\n    Environment          []corev1.EnvVar\n    Command, Args        []string\n    Resources            corev1.ResourceRequirements\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition\n    Ready      bool\n}\n```\n\n**Shared Types:**\n```go\ntype ProtocolType string   // \"HTTP\", \"HTTPS\"\ntype AuthModeType string   // \"picod\", \"none\"\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string\n    Name       string\n    Port       uint32       // required (no omitempty)\n    Protocol   ProtocolType\n}\n```\n\n**Constants:**\n```go\nconst AnnotationKeyRuntime = \"agentcube.io/runtime\"\nconst AnnotationKeyVersion = \"agentcube.io/version\"\n```\n\n**GroupVersion:**\n```go\nGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{\n    Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n    Version: \"v1alpha1\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. AR (Architecture Record) Change Directories\n\nEach AR directory follows a consistent 4-file pattern:\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `proposal.md` | Overview, scope, impact analysis, alternatives, acceptance criteria |\n| `delta-spec.md` | Requirements in Gherkin format (GIVEN/WHEN/THEN) |\n| `design.md` | Detailed architecture, data structures, API contracts, error handling, test strategy, implementation steps |\n| `tasks.md` | Granular task checklist with sub-tasks and acceptance criteria |\n\n**AR Inventory:**\n\n| AR | Title | Module | Status |\n|----|-------|--------|--------|\n| AR-001 | CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition | `pkg/apis` | Types implemented |\n| AR-002 | CRD CodeInterpreter Type Definition | `pkg/apis` | Types implemented |\n| AR-003 | CRD Shared Types and Constants | `pkg/apis` | Types implemented |\n| AR-004 | WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework | `pkg/workloadmanager` | Partially implemented (response/ only) |\n| AR-005 | Sandbox Creation Handler | `pkg/workloadmanager` | Not started |\n\n---\n\n### 6. Spec File Patterns\n\n#### 6.1 Root-Level Specs (`/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/`)\n\nThese are **OpenSpec-format** specifications, each with a `spec.md` and optional `design.md`:\n\n| Directory | Files |\n|-----------|-------|\n| `specs/code-execution/` | `spec.md`, `design.md` |\n| `specs/sandbox-orchestration/` | `spec.md`, `design.md` |\n| `specs/session-store/` | `spec.md`, `design.md` |\n| `specs/deployment/` | `spec.md`, `design.md`, `client-go.md` |\n| `specs/session-routing/` | `spec.md`, `design.md` |\n| `specs/cli-toolkit/` | `spec.md`, `design.md` |\n| `specs/python-sdk/` | `spec.md`, `design.md` |\n| `specs/ci-cd/` | `spec.md`, `design.md` |\n| `specs/idle-cleanup/` | `spec.md`, `design.md` |\n| `specs/integrations/` | `spec.md`, `design.md` |\n| `specs/testing/` | `agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` |\n| `specs/project.md` | Project context (tech stack, architecture, conventions) |\n\n#### 6.2 OpenSpec Spec Format Pattern\n\n```markdown\n# <Feature Name> Specification\n\n## Purpose\n<One paragraph describing what this spec covers>\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: <Requirement Name>\nThe system SHALL <requirement description using SHALL/SHOULD/MAY>.\n\n#### Scenario: <Scenario Name>\n- **GIVEN** <precondition>\n- **WHEN** <action>\n- **THEN** <expected outcome>\n- **AND** <additional outcome>\n```\n\n#### 6.3 Delta-Spec Format Pattern (for AR changes)\n\n```markdown\n# AR-XXX: <Title> -- Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n<One paragraph>\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: <Requirement Name>\nThe system SHALL <description>.\n\n#### Scenario: <Scenario Name>\n- **GIVEN** <precondition>\n- **WHEN** <action>\n- **THEN** <expected outcome>\n```\n\n#### 6.4 Proposal Format Pattern\n\n```markdown\n# AR-XXX: <Title>\n\n## Overview\n## 元信息 (Module, Language, Size)\n## 目的 (Purpose)\n## 范围 (In Scope / Out of Scope)\n## 影响分析 (Impact Analysis - direct, downstream, no-impact)\n## 备选方案 (Alternatives with rationale)\n## 验收标准 (Acceptance Criteria)\n## 状态 (Checklist)\n```\n\n#### 6.5 Design Document Format Pattern\n\n```markdown\n# AR-XXX: <Title> -- Design\n\n## 1. Architecture (positioning, package structure, dependencies)\n## 2. Data Structures (Go types with code examples)\n## 3. API Contract (route tables, request/response schemas, middleware chain)\n## 4. Error Handling (error categories, K8s error mapping, panic recovery)\n## 5. Test Strategy (test layers, test case matrix, fake client patterns, coverage targets)\n## 6. Implementation Steps (file creation order, key implementation details, verification checklist)\n## 7. Risks and Mitigations\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. Key File Paths Summary\n\n**Workspace root:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/`\n\n**pkg/workloadmanager (existing):**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/response/response.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/response/response_test.go`\n\n**pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 (all existing):**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n\n**AR-004 change docs:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md` (TODO placeholder)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/design.md` (comprehensive, 636 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md` (17 tasks, 255 lines)\n\n**Root-level delta-spec:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` (227 lines, AR-004 workloadmanager HTTP service)\n\n**Reference specs:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/code-execution/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/session-store/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/deployment/spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md`\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2892332bfffeO47eiC9tfqfrRY","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start"