{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775815864605,"sessionID":"ses_289236096ffeVNwHYTDZO0EFx7","part":{"id":"prt_d76dfac94001L0vxyhvSvSVtEm","messageID":"msg_d76df9a15001MuPbWdIstsoPWn","sessionID":"ses_289236096ffeVNwHYTDZO0EFx7","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7c45bcaf9cfb46ffa6d79410","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: <!-- TODO: 填写 Purpose -->\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: <!-- TODO: 填写 Requirements (Gherkin 格式) -->\n\n(End of file - total 9 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写 Purpose -->\n\n## Requirements\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写 Requirements (Gherkin 格式) -->","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775815864595,"end":1775815864604}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775815865973,"sessionID":"ses_289236096ffeVNwHYTDZO0EFx7","part":{"id":"prt_d76dfb1eb001wKREDsYtT2B7j4","messageID":"msg_d76df9a15001MuPbWdIstsoPWn","sessionID":"ses_289236096ffeVNwHYTDZO0EFx7","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_d1cc97a758964dfa9c3100b8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 — 设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位\n6: \n7: WorkloadManager 是 AgentCube 控制面的核心 HTTP 服务，负责管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 资源的完整生命周期。它作为 Kubernetes API 的封装层，向 Router、CLI 工具和 Python SDK 等下游消费者提供标准化的 RESTful 接口。\n8: \n9: 与 Router（session-routing）和 PicoD（code-execution）的关系：\n10: - **Router** 通过 HTTP 调用 WorkloadManager 的 `/api/v1/agentruntimes` 和 `/api/v1/codeinterpreters` 端点创建/销毁沙箱\n11: - **PicoD** 运行在沙箱容器内，与控制面 HTTP 服务无直接依赖\n12: - WorkloadManager **不** 负责 JWT 鉴权（Router 层负责）、Redis 状态管理（Session Store 负责）或代码执行（PicoD 负责）\n13: \n14: ### 1.2 包结构\n15: \n16: ```\n17: pkg/workloadmanager/\n18: ├── server.go                    # Server struct, NewServer(), Run(), Shutdown()\n19: ├── config.go                    # Config struct, 默认值, 环境变量读取\n20: ├── routes.go                    # SetupRoutes(engine *gin.Engine, deps *Dependencies)\n21: ├── handler/\n22: │   ├── health.go                # GET /healthz, GET /readyz\n23: │   ├── agent_runtime.go         # AgentRuntime CRUD handlers\n24: │   └── code_interpreter.go      # CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers\n25: ├── middleware/\n26: │   └── request_id.go            # X-Request-ID 追踪中间件\n27: ├── response/\n28: │   └── response.go              # JSON(), Error(), Created() 响应 helper\n29: ├── server_test.go               # Server 生命周期测试\n30: ├── config_test.go               # Config 默认值和环境变量测试\n31: ├── routes_test.go               # 路由注册完整性测试\n32: ├── handler/\n33: │   ├── health_test.go\n34: │   ├── agent_runtime_test.go\n35: │   └── code_interpreter_test.go\n36: └── response/\n37:     └── response_test.go\n38: ```\n39: \n40: ### 1.3 依赖关系\n41: \n42: ```\n43: pkg/workloadmanager/\n44: ├── 消费 → pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1          # CRD 类型定义 (AR-001/AR-002/AR-003)\n45: ├── 消费 → github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go  # 生成的 typed client, informers, listers\n46: ├── 消费 → github.com/gin-gonic/gin           # HTTP 框架 (新增依赖)\n47: ├── 消费 → k8s.io/client-go/rest              # Kubernetes REST config\n48: ├── 消费 → k8s.io/client-go/tools/clientcmd   # kubeconfig 解析\n49: ├── 被消费 → cmd/workload-manager/main.go     # 服务启动入口 (后续创建)\n50: └── 被消费 → session-routing (Router)         # 通过 HTTP API 调用沙箱管理端点\n51: ```\n52: \n53: 依赖图：\n54: ```\n55: Router ──HTTP──→ WorkloadManager ──typed client──→ Kubernetes API Server\n56: CLI   ──HTTP──→                     ↕\n57: SDK   ──HTTP──→                informer cache (read-only)\n58: ```\n59: \n60: ---\n61: \n62: ## 2. 数据结构\n63: \n64: ### 2.1 Config\n65: \n66: ```go\n67: type Config struct {\n68:     Port         int    // 监听端口，默认 8080\n69:     KubeConfig   string // kubeconfig 路径，空字符串表示 in-cluster config\n70:     Namespace    string // 默认操作的命名空间，可被请求参数覆盖\n71:     ResyncPeriod time.Duration // informer 重同步周期，默认 30s\n72: }\n73: \n74: func DefaultConfig() *Config\n75: func LoadConfig() (*Config, error)  // 从环境变量读取，支持 WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT 等\n76: ```\n77: \n78: 环境变量映射：\n79: | 变量 | 字段 | 默认值 |\n80: |------|------|--------|\n81: | `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_PORT` | Port | 8080 |\n82: | `KUBECONFIG` | KubeConfig | \"\" (in-cluster) |\n83: | `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_NAMESPACE` | Namespace | \"default\" |\n84: | `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_RESYNC_PERIOD` | ResyncPeriod | 30s |\n85: \n86: ### 2.2 Server\n87: \n88: ```go\n89: type Server struct {\n90:     config  *Config\n91:     engine  *gin.Engine\n92:     httpSrv *http.Server\n93:     deps    *Dependencies\n94: }\n95: \n96: type Dependencies struct {\n97:     Clientset   clientset.Interface              // typed client for writes\n98:     Informer    informers.SharedInformerFactory  // informer factory for reads\n99:     ARLister    runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n100:     CILister    runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister\n101: }\n102: ```\n103: \n104: **生命周期方法：**\n105: - `NewServer(cfg *Config) (*Server, error)` — 构造 Server，初始化 gin engine、Kubernetes client、informer factory\n106: - `Run(ctx context.Context) error` — 启动 informer 缓存等待同步，然后启动 HTTP server，阻塞直到 ctx 取消\n107: - `Shutdown(ctx context.Context) error` — 调用 `http.Server.Shutdown()` 优雅停机\n108: \n109: ### 2.3 请求/响应 DTO\n110: \n111: **创建请求体** (AgentRuntime / CodeInterpreter 共用模式)：\n112: ```go\n113: // 直接使用 v1alpha1.AgentRuntime / v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter 作为请求体\n114: // 通过 gin.ShouldBindJSON() 反序列化\n115: ```\n116: \n117: **统一成功响应**：\n118: ```go\n119: type SuccessResponse struct {\n120:     Data   interface{} `json:\"data\"`\n121:     Message string    `json:\"message,omitempty\"`\n122: }\n123: ```\n124: \n125: **统一错误响应**：\n126: ```go\n127: type ErrorResponse struct {\n128:     Error   string `json:\"error\"`\n129:     Code    int    `json:\"code\"`\n130:     RequestID string `json:\"request_id,omitempty\"`\n131: }\n132: ```\n133: \n134: ### 2.4 Informer 缓存策略\n135: \n136: 根据 REQ-006，读写分离策略：\n137: \n138: | 操作 | 数据源 | 理由 |\n139: |------|--------|------|\n140: | GET 列表 | Informer Lister | 低延迟，避免频繁 API 调用 |\n141: | GET 单个 | Informer Lister | 低延迟，缓存命中率高 |\n142: | POST 创建 | Typed Client (直接 API) | 需要立即持久化 |\n143: | PUT 更新 | Typed Client (直接 API) | 需要 resourceVersion 一致性 |\n144: | DELETE 删除 | Typed Client (直接 API) | 需要立即生效 |\n145: \n146: Informer 启动流程：\n147: 1. `NewServer()` 创建 `SharedInformerFactory` 并获取 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter informers\n148: 2. `Run()` 中调用 `factory.Start(ctx.Done())` 启动 informer\n149: 3. 调用 `factory.WaitForCacheSync(ctx.Done())` 等待缓存同步完成\n150: 4. 缓存同步完成后才标记 readyz 为就绪\n151: \n152: ---\n153: \n154: ## 3. API 契约\n155: \n156: ### 3.1 路由表\n157: \n158: | Method | Path | Handler | 说明 |\n159: |--------|------|---------|------|\n160: | GET | `/healthz` | `health.HealthzHandler` | 存活探针，始终返回 200 |\n161: | GET | `/readyz` | `health.ReadyzHandler` | 就绪探针，检查 informer 缓存同步状态 |\n162: | POST | `/api/v1/agentruntimes` | `handler.CreateAgentRuntime` | 创建 AgentRuntime |\n163: | GET | `/api/v1/agentruntimes` | `handler.ListAgentRuntimes` | 列出 AgentRuntime |\n164: | GET | `/api/v1/agentruntimes/:name` | `handler.GetAgentRuntime` | 获取单个 AgentRuntime |\n165: | PUT | `/api/v1/agentruntimes/:name` | `handler.UpdateAgentRuntime` | 更新 AgentRuntime |\n166: | DELETE | `/api/v1/agentruntimes/:name` | `handler.DeleteAgentRuntime` | 删除 AgentRuntime |\n167: | POST | `/api/v1/codeinterpreters` | `handler.CreateCodeInterpreter` | 创建 CodeInterpreter |\n168: | GET | `/api/v1/codeinterpreters` | `handler.ListCodeInterpreters` | 列出 CodeInterpreter |\n169: | GET | `/api/v1/codeinterpreters/:name` | `handler.GetCodeInterpreter` | 获取单个 CodeInterpreter |\n170: | PUT | `/api/v1/codeinterpreters/:name` | `handler.UpdateCodeInterpreter` | 更新 CodeInterpreter |\n171: | DELETE | `/api/v1/codeinterpreters/:name` | `handler.DeleteCodeInterpreter` | 删除 CodeInterpreter |\n172: \n173: ### 3.2 公共请求参数\n174: \n175: 所有 CRUD 端点支持以下查询参数：\n176: \n177: | 参数 | 类型 | 必填 | 说明 |\n178: |------|------|------|------|\n179: | `namespace` | string | 是 | 目标 Kubernetes 命名空间 |\n180: \n181: ### 3.3 端点详细规范\n182: \n183: #### GET /healthz\n184: \n185: **响应 (200 OK)：**\n186: ```json\n187: { \"status\": \"ok\" }\n188: ```\n189: \n190: 始终返回 200，不依赖任何外部服务状态。用于 Kubernetes liveness probe。\n191: \n192: #### GET /readyz\n193: \n194: **响应 (200 OK) — 就绪：**\n195: ```json\n196: { \"status\": \"ready\" }\n197: ```\n198: \n199: **响应 (503 Service Unavailable) — 未就绪：**\n200: ```json\n201: { \"status\": \"not_ready\", \"reason\": \"informer cache not synced\" }\n202: ```\n203: \n204: 检查 `informerFactory.WaitForCacheSync()` 的结果。用于 Kubernetes readiness probe。\n205: \n206: #### POST /api/v1/agentruntimes\n207: \n208: **请求体：**\n209: ```json\n210: {\n211:   \"metadata\": {\n212:     \"name\": \"my-runtime\",\n213:     \"namespace\": \"default\",\n214:     \"labels\": { \"app\": \"sandbox\" }\n215:   },\n216:   \"spec\": {\n217:     \"podTemplate\": {\n218:       \"spec\": {\n219:         \"containers\": [{\n220:           \"name\": \"agent\",\n221:           \"image\": \"agentcube/agent:latest\"\n222:         }]\n223:       }\n224:     }\n225:   }\n226: }\n227: ```\n228: \n229: **查询参数：** `namespace` (可选，请求体中的 metadata.namespace 优先)\n230: \n231: **成功响应 (201 Created)：**\n232: ```json\n233: {\n234:   \"data\": {\n235:     \"metadata\": {\n236:       \"name\": \"my-runtime\",\n237:       \"uid\": \"abc-123\",\n238:       \"creationTimestamp\": \"2026-04-10T07:00:00Z\"\n239:     },\n240:     \"spec\": { ... },\n241:     \"status\": {}\n242:   }\n243: }\n244: ```\n245: \n246: **错误响应：**\n247: - `400` — 请求体缺少 `metadata.name` 或 `spec.podTemplate`\n248: - `400` — 缺少 `namespace` 参数且请求体中无 `metadata.namespace`\n249: - `400` — 无效的 JSON 格式\n250: - `409` — 资源已存在 (Kubernetes AlreadyExists 错误)\n251: - `500` — 内部服务器错误\n252: \n253: #### GET /api/v1/agentruntimes\n254: \n255: **查询参数：** `namespace` (必填)\n256: \n257: **成功响应 (200 OK)：**\n258: ```json\n259: {\n260:   \"data\": {\n261:     \"items\": [\n262:       { \"metadata\": { \"name\": \"runtime-1\" }, \"spec\": { ... }, \"status\": {} },\n263:       { \"metadata\": { \"name\": \"runtime-2\" }, \"spec\": { ... }, \"status\": {} }\n264:     ]\n265:   }\n266: }\n267: ```\n268: \n269: **错误响应：**\n270: - `400` — 缺少 `namespace` 参数\n271: - `500` — 内部服务器错误\n272: \n273: #### GET /api/v1/agentruntimes/:name\n274: \n275: **查询参数：** `namespace` (必填)\n276: \n277: **成功响应 (200 OK)：** 单个 AgentRuntime 对象\n278: \n279: **错误响应：**\n280: - `400` — 缺少 `namespace` 参数\n281: - `404` — 资源不存在\n282: - `500` — 内部服务器错误\n283: \n284: #### PUT /api/v1/agentruntimes/:name\n285: \n286: **请求体：** 完整的 AgentRuntime 对象（需包含 `metadata.resourceVersion`）\n287: \n288: **查询参数：** `namespace` (必填)\n289: \n290: **成功响应 (200 OK)：** 更新后的 AgentRuntime 对象\n291: \n292: **错误响应：**\n293: - `400` — 缺少 `namespace` 参数或请求体无效\n294: - `404` — 资源不存在\n295: - `409` — resourceVersion 冲突\n296: - `500` — 内部服务器错误\n297: \n298: #### DELETE /api/v1/agentruntimes/:name\n299: \n300: **查询参数：** `namespace` (必填)\n301: \n302: **成功响应 (200 OK)：**\n303: ```json\n304: { \"data\": { \"message\": \"agentruntime 'my-runtime' deleted\" } }\n305: ```\n306: \n307: **错误响应：**\n308: - `400` — 缺少 `namespace` 参数\n309: - `404` — 资源不存在\n310: - `500` — 内部服务器错误\n311: \n312: #### CodeInterpreter 端点\n313: \n314: 与 AgentRuntime 端点结构完全对称，路径前缀替换为 `/api/v1/codeinterpreters`，类型替换为 `v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter`。\n315: \n316: ### 3.4 中间件链\n317: \n318: ```\n319: Request → gin.Recovery() → gin.Logger() → RequestIDMiddleware → Handler\n320: ```\n321: \n322: | 中间件 | 职责 | 实现方式 |\n323: |--------|------|----------|\n324: | `gin.Recovery()` | 捕获 panic，返回 500 | 复用 Gin 内置 |\n325: | `gin.Logger()` | 记录请求方法、路径、状态码、延迟 | 复用 Gin 内置 |\n326: | `RequestIDMiddleware` | 生成/透传 `X-Request-ID`，注入到错误响应中 | 自定义，使用 `ulid` 或 `uuid` |\n327: \n328: Request ID 生成策略：优先读取请求头 `X-Request-ID`，若不存在则生成新的 UUID v4。\n329: \n330: ---\n331: \n332: ## 4. 错误处理\n333: \n334: ### 4.1 错误分类\n335: \n336: | 类别 | HTTP 状态码 | 错误码 | 示例 |\n337: |------|-------------|--------|------|\n338: | 客户端错误 — 参数缺失 | 400 | 40001 | `\"missing required parameter: namespace\"` |\n339: | 客户端错误 — 请求体无效 | 400 | 40002 | `\"invalid JSON: unexpected EOF\"` |\n340: | 客户端错误 — 验证失败 | 400 | 40003 | `\"spec.podTemplate is required\"` |\n341: | 资源不存在 | 404 | 40401 | `\"agentruntime 'my-runtime' not found\"` |\n342: | 资源冲突 | 409 | 40901 | `\"agentruntime 'my-runtime' already exists\"` |\n343: | 资源版本冲突 | 409 | 40902 | `\"conflict: resourceVersion mismatch\"` |\n344: | 服务器内部错误 | 500 | 50001 | `\"internal server error\"` |\n345: | Kubernetes API 错误 | 500 | 50002 | `\"kubernetes API error: connection refused\"` |\n346: \n347: ### 4.2 错误响应格式\n348: \n349: ```json\n350: {\n351:   \"error\": \"human-readable message\",\n352:   \"code\": 40001,\n353:   \"request_id\": \"01ARZ3NDEKTSV4RRFFQ69G5FAV\"\n354: }\n355: ```\n356: \n357: ### 4.3 Kubernetes 错误映射\n358: \n359: ```go\n360: func mapK8sError(err error) (int, int, string) {\n361:     switch {\n362:     case apierrors.IsNotFound(err):\n363:         return http.StatusNotFound, 40401, \"resource not found\"\n364:     case apierrors.IsAlreadyExists(err):\n365:         return http.StatusConflict, 40901, \"resource already exists\"\n366:     case apierrors.IsConflict(err):\n367:         return http.StatusConflict, 40902, \"resource version conflict\"\n368:     case apierrors.IsInvalid(err):\n369:         return http.StatusBadRequest, 40003, err.Error()\n370:     default:\n371:         return http.StatusInternalServerError, 50002, \"kubernetes API error\"\n372:     }\n373: }\n374: ```\n375: \n376: ### 4.4 Panic 恢复\n377: \n378: `gin.Recovery()` 捕获的 panic 将：\n379: 1. 记录完整 stack trace 到日志\n380: 2. 返回 `500 Internal Server Error`\n381: 3. 响应体包含 `{\"error\": \"internal server error\", \"code\": 50001}`\n382: 4. **不** 暴露 stack trace 给客户端（生产安全）\n383: \n384: ---\n385: \n386: ## 5. 测试策略\n387: \n388: ### 5.1 测试分层\n389: \n390: | 层级 | 测试对象 | 隔离方式 | 工具 |\n391: |------|----------|----------|------|\n392: | 单元 | Handler 函数 | Fake clientset + httptest | `testify/assert`, `gin.CreateTestContext()` |\n393: | 单元 | Response helper | 纯函数测试 | `testify/assert` |\n394: | 单元 | Config 默认值 | 无外部依赖 | `testify/assert` |\n395: | 集成 | Server 生命周期 | 随机可用端口 | `httptest.Server`, `testify/assert` |\n396: | 路由 | 路由注册完整性 | 无外部依赖 | `testify/assert` |\n397: \n398: ### 5.2 测试用例清单\n399: \n400: #### Server 生命周期 (`server_test.go`)\n401: \n402: | 测试名称 | 场景 | 验证点 |\n403: |----------|------|--------|\n404: | `TestNewServer_DefaultConfig` | 使用默认配置创建 Server | 端口 8080, gin.ReleaseMode, 非空 deps |\n405: | `TestNewServer_DebugMode` | Config.Debug=true | gin.DebugMode |\n406: | `TestServer_RunAndShutdown` | 启动后立即关闭 | 无 panic, 端口释放 |\n407: | `TestServer_PortConflict` | 端口已被占用 | 返回错误, 不阻塞 |\n408: \n409: #### Config (`config_test.go`)\n410: \n411: | 测试名称 | 场景 | 验证点 |\n412: |----------|------|--------|\n413: | `TestDefaultConfig` | 调用 DefaultConfig() | Port=8080, 空 KubeConfig |\n414: | `TestLoadConfig_FromEnv` | 设置环境变量后调用 | 读取环境变量值 |\n415: | `TestLoadConfig_Defaults` | 无环境变量 | 使用默认值 |\n416: \n417: #### Health Handler (`handler/health_test.go`)\n418: \n419: | 测试名称 | 场景 | 验证点 |\n420: |----------|------|--------|\n421: | `TestHealthzHandler` | GET /healthz | 200, `{\"status\": \"ok\"}` |\n422: | `TestReadyzHandler_Ready` | Informer 已同步 | 200, `{\"status\": \"ready\"}` |\n423: | `TestReadyzHandler_NotReady` | Informer 未同步 | 503, `{\"status\": \"not_ready\"}` |\n424: \n425: #### AgentRuntime Handler (`handler/agent_runtime_test.go`)\n426: \n427: | 测试名称 | 场景 | 验证点 |\n428: |----------|------|--------|\n429: | `TestCreateAgentRuntime_Success` | 合法请求 | 201, 返回创建的資源 |\n430: | `TestCreateAgentRuntime_MissingName` | 请求体无 metadata.name | 400, 错误信息指明缺失字段 |\n431: | `TestCreateAgentRuntime_MissingPodTemplate` | 请求体无 spec.podTemplate | 400 |\n432: | `TestCreateAgentRuntime_MissingNamespace` | 无 namespace 参数 | 400 |\n433: | `TestCreateAgentRuntime_InvalidJSON` | 非法 JSON | 400 |\n434: | `TestCreateAgentRuntime_AlreadyExists` | 重复创建同名资源 | 409 |\n435: | `TestListAgentRuntimes_Success` | 命名空间下有资源 | 200, 返回 items 列表 |\n436: | `TestListAgentRuntimes_MissingNamespace` | 无 namespace 参数 | 400 |\n437: | `TestGetAgentRuntime_Success` | 资源存在 | 200, 返回完整对象 |\n438: | `TestGetAgentRuntime_NotFound` | 资源不存在 | 404 |\n439: | `TestUpdateAgentRuntime_Success` | 合法更新 | 200, resourceVersion 变更 |\n440: | `TestUpdateAgentRuntime_NotFound` | 更新不存在的资源 | 404 |\n441: | `TestUpdateAgentRuntime_Conflict` | resourceVersion 过期 | 409 |\n442: | `TestDeleteAgentRuntime_Success` | 资源存在 | 200 |\n443: | `TestDeleteAgentRuntime_NotFound` | 资源不存在 | 404 |\n444: \n445: #### CodeInterpreter Handler (`handler/code_interpreter_test.go`)\n446: \n447: 与 AgentRuntime 测试对称，覆盖相同场景。\n448: \n449: #### Response Helper (`response/response_test.go`)\n450: \n451: | 测试名称 | 场景 | 验证点 |\n452: |----------|------|--------|\n453: | `TestJSON_Success` | 正常响应 | 200, Content-Type=application/json |\n454: | `TestCreated_Success` | 创建成功 | 201, 响应体包含 data |\n455: | `TestError_BadRequest` | 客户端错误 | 400, 错误格式正确 |\n456: | `TestError_NotFound` | 资源不存在 | 404 |\n457: | `TestError_Internal` | 服务器错误 | 500 |\n458: | `TestError_WithRequestID` | 带 Request ID | 响应体包含 request_id |\n459: \n460: #### Routes (`routes_test.go`)\n461: \n462: | 测试名称 | 场景 | 验证点 |\n463: |----------|------|--------|\n464: | `TestSetupRoutes_HealthEndpoints` | 注册健康端点 | /healthz, /readyz 可访问 |\n465: | `TestSetupRoutes_AgentRuntimeRoutes` | 注册 AgentRuntime 路由 | 5 个端点均可路由 |\n466: | `TestSetupRoutes_CodeInterpreterRoutes` | 注册 CodeInterpreter 路由 | 5 个端点均可路由 |\n467: | `TestSetupRoutes_404ForUnknown` | 访问未注册路径 | 404 |\n468: \n469: ### 5.3 Fake Clientset 使用模式\n470: \n471: ```go\n472: func TestCreateAgentRuntime_Success(t *testing.T) {\n473:     // 1. 创建 fake clientset\n474:     clientset := fakeclientset.NewSimpleClientset()\n475:     \n476:     // 2. 构造 handler 依赖\n477:     handler := NewAgentRuntimeHandler(clientset)\n478:     \n479:     // 3. 构造测试请求\n480:     w, ctx := gin.CreateTestContext(httptest.NewRecorder())\n481:     req := httptest.NewRequest(\"POST\", \"/api/v1/agentruntimes?namespace=default\",\n482:         strings.NewReader(`{\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"test\"},\"spec\":{\"podTemplate\":{\"spec\":{\"containers\":[{\"name\":\"c\",\"image\":\"img\"}]}}}}`))\n483:     req.Header.Set(\"Content-Type\", \"application/json\")\n484:     ctx.Request = req\n485:     \n486:     // 4. 调用 handler\n487:     handler.Create(ctx)\n488:     \n489:     // 5. 验证响应\n490:     assert.Equal(t, 201, w.Code)\n491:     var resp map[string]interface{}\n492:     json.Unmarshal(w.Body.Bytes(), &resp)\n493:     assert.Contains(t, resp, \"data\")\n494: }\n495: ```\n496: \n497: ### 5.4 测试覆盖率目标\n498: \n499: - **行覆盖率**: ≥ 80%\n500: - **分支覆盖率**: ≥ 70%\n501: - **T/C 比率**: > 0.4 (符合 `testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` 要求)\n502: \n503: ### 5.5 测试执行\n504: \n505: ```bash\n506: # 运行全部测试\n507: go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v\n508: \n509: # 带覆盖率\n510: go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -coverprofile=coverage.out\n511: go tool cover -html=coverage.out\n512: \n513: # 运行单个测试\n514: go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handler/ -run TestCreateAgentRuntime_Success -v\n515: ```\n516: \n517: ---\n518: \n519: ## 6. 实现步骤\n520: \n521: ### 6.1 文件创建顺序\n522: \n523: 按依赖自底向上实现，确保每一步都可编译：\n524: \n525: | 步骤 | 文件 | 说明 | 验证 |\n526: |------|------|------|------|\n527: | 1 | `go.mod` 添加 gin | `go get github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | `go mod tidy` 无错误 |\n528: | 2 | `response/response.go` | 响应 helper，无外部依赖 | `go build` |\n529: | 3 | `response/response_test.go` | 响应 helper 测试 | `go test` |\n530: | 4 | `config.go` | Config struct + 默认值 | `go build` |\n531: | 5 | `config_test.go` | Config 测试 | `go test` |\n532: | 6 | `handler/health.go` | 健康检查 handler | `go build` |\n533: | 7 | `handler/health_test.go` | 健康检查测试 | `go test` |\n534: | 8 | `handler/agent_runtime.go` | AgentRuntime CRUD handlers | `go build` |\n535: | 9 | `handler/agent_runtime_test.go` | AgentRuntime 测试 | `go test` |\n536: | 10 | `handler/code_interpreter.go` | CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers | `go build` |\n537: | 11 | `handler/code_interpreter_test.go` | CodeInterpreter 测试 | `go test` |\n538: | 12 | `middleware/request_id.go` | Request ID 中间件 | `go build` |\n539: | 13 | `routes.go` | 路由注册 | `go build` |\n540: | 14 | `routes_test.go` | 路由测试 | `go test` |\n541: | 15 | `server.go` | Server struct + Run/Shutdown | `go build` |\n542: | 16 | `server_test.go` | Server 生命周期测试 | `go test` |\n543: | 17 | 全量测试 | `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v` | 全部通过 |\n544: | 18 | `go mod tidy` | 清理依赖 | 无冲突 |\n545: \n546: ### 6.2 关键实现细节\n547: \n548: #### Server.Run() 启动流程\n549: \n550: ```go\n551: func (s *Server) Run(ctx context.Context) error {\n552:     // 1. 启动 informer\n553:     s.deps.Informer.Start(ctx.Done())\n554:     \n555:     // 2. 等待缓存同步\n556:     if !s.deps.Informer.WaitForCacheSync(ctx.Done()) {\n557:         return fmt.Errorf(\"informer cache sync failed\")\n558:     }\n559:     s.ready.Store(true)  // 标记就绪\n560:     \n561:     // 3. 启动 HTTP server\n562:     errCh := make(chan error, 1)\n563:     go func() {\n564:         errCh <- s.httpSrv.ListenAndServe()\n565:     }()\n566:     \n567:     // 4. 等待 ctx 取消或 server 错误\n568:     select {\n569:     case <-ctx.Done():\n570:         return s.Shutdown(context.Background())\n571:     case err := <-errCh:\n572:         if err == http.ErrServerClosed {\n573:             return nil\n574:         }\n575:         return err\n576:     }\n577: }\n578: ```\n579: \n580: #### Handler 命名空间解析\n581: \n582: 所有 CRUD handler 统一使用以下逻辑解析 namespace：\n583: \n584: ```go\n585: func getNamespace(c *gin.Context) (string, error) {\n586:     ns := c.Query(\"namespace\")\n587:     if ns == \"\" {\n588:         return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"missing required parameter: namespace\")\n589:     }\n590:     return ns, nil\n591: }\n592: ```\n593: \n594: #### AgentRuntime 创建验证\n595: \n596: ```go\n597: func validateAgentRuntime(ar *v1alpha1.AgentRuntime) error {\n598:     if ar.Name == \"\" {\n599:         return fmt.Errorf(\"metadata.name is required\")\n600:     }\n601:     if ar.Spec.Template == nil {\n602:         return fmt.Errorf(\"spec.podTemplate is required\")\n603:     }\n604:     return nil\n605: }\n606: ```\n607: \n608: ### 6.3 验证检查清单\n609: \n610: - [ ] `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过\n611: - [ ] `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v` 全部通过\n612: - [ ] `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` 已添加到 `go.mod` 且 `go mod tidy` 无冲突\n613: - [ ] 服务启动后监听配置的端口（默认 8080）\n614: - [ ] `GET /healthz` 返回 `200 OK` 且响应体为 `{\"status\": \"ok\"}`\n615: - [ ] `GET /readyz` 在 informer 同步后返回 `200`，同步前返回 `503`\n616: - [ ] `POST /api/v1/agentruntimes` 接收合法请求返回 `201`\n617: - [ ] `POST /api/v1/agentruntimes` 缺少 `podTemplate` 返回 `400`\n618: - [ ] `POST /api/v1/codeinterpreters` 接收合法请求返回 `201`\n619: - [ ] 相同 name 的连续创建请求返回 `409 Conflict`\n620: - [ ] 服务支持优雅关闭（收到 SIGTERM 后完成现有请求再退出）\n621: - [ ] Gin 模式在 Debug=false 时为 ReleaseMode，true 时为 DebugMode\n622: - [ ] 所有 handler 使用统一的 JSON 错误响应格式\n623: - [ ] 测试覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n624: - [ ] T/C 比率 > 0.4\n625: \n626: ---\n627: \n628: ## 7. 风险与缓解\n629: \n630: | 风险 | 影响 | 缓解措施 |\n631: |------|------|----------|\n632: | Informer 缓存同步延迟 | 启动后短时间内 GET 请求可能返回空列表 | readyz 在缓存同步完成前返回 503，Kubernetes 不会将流量路由到未就绪的 Pod |\n633: | Fake clientset 与真实 API 行为差异 | 测试通过但生产环境行为不同 | 使用 `k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/fake` 标准 fake，行为与真实 API 高度一致；后续补充 E2E 测试 |\n634: | Gin 依赖引入 | 增加模块依赖面 | Gin 是 Go 生态最成熟的 HTTP 框架之一，已被 Router 组件选用，团队已有使用经验 |\n635: | Namespace 参数遗漏 | 操作错误的命名空间 | 所有 handler 统一通过 `getNamespace()` 获取，强制校验 |\n636: | ResourceVersion 冲突 | 并发更新导致 409 | 客户端需实现重试逻辑（带 backoff）；WorkloadManager 返回明确的冲突错误信息 |\n\n(End of file - total 636 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 — 设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构\n\n### 1.1 定位\n\nWorkloadManager 是 AgentCube 控制面的核心 HTTP 服务，负责管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 资源的完整生命周期。它作为 Kubernetes API 的封装层，向 Router、CLI 工具和 Python SDK 等下游消费者提供标准化的 RESTful 接口。\n\n与 Router（session-routing）和 PicoD（code-execution）的关系：\n- **Router** 通过 HTTP 调用 WorkloadManager 的 `/api/v1/agentruntimes` 和 `/api/v1/codeinterpreters` 端点创建/销毁沙箱\n- **PicoD** 运行在沙箱容器内，与控制面 HTTP 服务无直接依赖\n- WorkloadManager **不** 负责 JWT 鉴权（Router 层负责）、Redis 状态管理（Session Store 负责）或代码执行（PicoD 负责）\n\n### 1.2 包结构\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n├── server.go                    # Server struct, NewServer(), Run(), Shutdown()\n├── config.go                    # Config struct, 默认值, 环境变量读取\n├── routes.go                    # SetupRoutes(engine *gin.Engine, deps *Dependencies)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","time":{"start":1775815865962,"end":1775815865970}}}}
